{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "qa-control-center-api",
    "name": "QA Control Center API",
    "description": "Coleção completa para testar a API QA Control Center\n\n## 🔐 PRIMEIRO USO\n\n1. ⚠️ **Configure REGISTER_TOKEN**:\n   - Abra Collection → Variables\n   - Localize `register_token`\n   - Paste o valor do seu .env REGISTER_TOKEN\n\n2. 📝 **Registre um usuário**:\n   - Execute: Auth → 1️⃣ Register User\n   - Use email/password desejados\n\n3. 🔓 **Faça Login**:\n   - Execute: Auth → 2️⃣ Login\n   - JWT será salvo automaticamente em `{{jwt_token}}`\n\n4. ✅ **Teste qualquer endpoint protegido**:\n   - Todos agora têm Authorization automática\n   - Colinha JWT é injetado automaticamente",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Autenticação",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register User",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "    const response = pm.response.json();",
                  "    console.log('Usuário registrado:', response.email);",
                  "    console.log('Próximo passo: Fazer Login');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "x-register-token",
                "value": "{{register_token}}",
                "type": "text",
                "description": "Token de registro do .env"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"QA Tester\",\n  \"email\": \"tester@qa.dev\",\n  \"password\": \"Test@1234\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/register",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "register"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const response = pm.response.json();",
                  "",
                  "if (response.token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('jwt_token', response.token);",
                  "    console.log('Login bem-sucedido!');",
                  "    console.log('JWT salvo em {{jwt_token}}');",
                  "    console.log('Agora teste qualquer endpoint protegido!');",
                  "} else {",
                  "    console.log('Nenhum token na resposta');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"tester@qa.dev\",\n  \"password\": \"Test@1234\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "login"]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
